  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You now add your Wisdom modifier to the damage you deal with any Cleric cantrip.</p><p>Alternatively, once on each of your turns when you hit a creature with a weapon attack, you can cause the attack to deal an extra 1d8 Radiant damage. At Cleric level 14, the extra damage on weapon attacks increases to 2d8.</p><section class=\"secret\" id=\"secret-A4TDvnBnvmiUVCXF\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>When you get this feature, you will need to edit your cantrips (and any future cantrips) to reflect this. In the \"Details\" section on each cantrip, under \"Spell Effects\" paste this into the \"Damage Formula\" text box: <span style=\"font-family:Courier\">+ @abilities.wis.mod</span></p></section>",
